'''卡拉·玛丽·劳森'''（{{lang-en|Kara Marie Lawson}}，{{bd|1981年|2月14日||}}）生于弗吉尼亚州亚历山德里亚，是一名美国退役女子篮球运动员、教练及体育解说员。她于1999年至2003年间代表田纳西大学校队参加校际比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/womens-college-basketball/story/_/id/29446824/duke-hires-kara-lawson-women-basketball-coach|title=Duke hires Kara Lawson as women's basketball coach|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2020-07-12|accessdate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200902143748/https://www.espn.com/womens-college-basketball/story/_/id/29446824/duke-hires-kara-lawson-women-basketball-coach|archivedate=2020-09-02}}</ref>。2008年北京奥运随[[美国国家女子篮球队|国家队]]参赛并收获金牌<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/la/kara-lawson-1.html|title=Kara Lawson|work=Sport Reference|accessdate=2021-03-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418051213/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/la/kara-lawson-1.html|archivedate=2020-04-18}}</ref>。

劳森在成为职业选手数年后便已开始从事篮球解说工作<ref name="ESPNMedia">{{Cite web|url=http://www.espnmediazone3.com/us/2010/04/06/lawson_kara/|title=Kara Lawson:College Basketball and NBA Analyst|date=2010-04-06|access-date=2011-02-24|work=ESPN|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710202120/http://www.espnmediazone3.com/us/2010/04/06/lawson_kara/|archive-date=2011-07-10}}</ref>。2015年退役后，她一度专注于体育解说事业<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/dc-sports-bog/wp/2017/09/27/kara-lawson-will-replace-phil-chenier-as-wizards-primary-color-analyst/|title=Wizards make Kara Lawson one of the first female primary TV analysts for an NBA team|last=Steinberg|first=Dan|date=2017-09-27|work=[[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]]|access-date=2017-09-28|issn=0190-8286|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707004837/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/dc-sports-bog/wp/2017/09/27/kara-lawson-will-replace-phil-chenier-as-wizards-primary-color-analyst/|archivedate=2020-07-07}}</ref>。2019年，她在[[波士顿凯尔特人|波士顿凯尔特人]]队担任助理教练<ref name=":1"/>。2020年，她成为Duke Blue Devils女子篮球队的主教练<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Karalis|first=John|date=2020-07-13|title=Kara Lawson on leaving Celtics for Duke: 'It's been an emotional three days'|url=https://www.masslive.com/celtics/2020/07/kara-lawson-on-leaving-boston-celtics-for-duke-its-been-an-emotional-three-days-its-been-tough.html|access-date=2020-12-02|website=MassLive|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714044942/https://www.masslive.com/celtics/2020/07/kara-lawson-on-leaving-boston-celtics-for-duke-its-been-an-emotional-three-days-its-been-tough.html|archivedate=2020-07-14}}</ref>。

